{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":false,"flaws":{},"title":"Node.childNodes","mdn_url":"/de/docs/Web/API/Node/childNodes","locale":"de","native":"Deutsch","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/Node\"><code>Node</code></a></strong></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Eigenschaften</summary><ol><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Node/baseURI\"><code>baseURI</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><em><code>childNodes</code></em></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/Node/firstChild\"><code>firstChild</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Node/isConnected\"><code>isConnected</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/Node/lastChild\"><code>lastChild</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/Node/nextSibling\"><code>nextSibling</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Node/nodeName\"><code>nodeName</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Node/nodeType\"><code>nodeType</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/Node/nodeValue\"><code>nodeValue</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Node/ownerDocument\"><code>ownerDocument</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Node/parentElement\"><code>parentElement</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/Node/parentNode\"><code>parentNode</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/Node/previousSibling\"><code>previousSibling</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/Node/textContent\"><code>textContent</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Methoden</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/Node/appendChild\"><code>appendChild()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/Node/cloneNode\"><code>cloneNode()</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Node/compareDocumentPosition\"><code>compareDocumentPosition()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Node/contains\"><code>contains()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Node/getRootNode\"><code>getRootNode()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/Node/hasChildNodes\"><code>hasChildNodes()</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Node/insertBefore\"><code>insertBefore()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Node/isDefaultNamespace\"><code>isDefaultNamespace()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Node/isEqualNode\"><code>isEqualNode()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Node/isSameNode\"><code>isSameNode()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Node/isSupported\"><code>isSupported()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Node/lookupNamespaceURI\"><code>lookupNamespaceURI()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Node/lookupPrefix\"><code>lookupPrefix()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/Node/normalize\"><code>normalize()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/Node/removeChild\"><code>removeChild()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/Node/replaceChild\"><code>replaceChild()</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Vererbung:</summary><ol><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/EventTarget\"><code>EventTarget</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"summary","title":"Allgemein","isH3":true,"content":"<p><code>childNodes</code> gibt eine <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/NodeList\"><code>NodeList</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>, welche alle Kindknoten (<code>childNodes</code>) eines bestimmten HTML-Elements enthält, zurück.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"syntax","title":"Syntax","isH3":true,"content":"<pre class=\"eval notranslate\">var <var>nodeList</var> = referenzElement.childNodes;\n</pre>\n<p><var>nodeList</var> ist eine Liste, die alle Kindknoten eines bestimmten Elements der Reihenfolge nach enthält. Falls das Element keine Kindknoten enthält, gibt <code>childNodes</code> eine leere <code>NodeList</code> zurück.<br>\n <br>\n Diese Eigenschaft kann nur ausgelesen werden (read-only).</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"beispiel","title":"Beispiel","isH3":true,"content":"<p>Folgendes HTML-Dokument liegt vor:</p>\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush:html notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token doctype\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;!</span><span class=\"token doctype-tag\">DOCTYPE</span> <span class=\"token name\">html</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>html</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>body</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>h3</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>Neue Mitarbeiter eingestellt<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>h3</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>Dank der guten Konjunktur letzten Jahres [...]<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>body</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>html</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<p>Nun sollen die <code>childNodes</code> von <code>&lt;body&gt;</code> ausgelesen und in einer Liste namens <code><var>nodeList</var></code> gespeichert werden:</p>\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush:javascript notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> bd <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> document<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>body<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\">// Zuerst werden wir überprüfen, ob das &lt;body&gt;-Element überhaupt Kindknoten hat.</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">if</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>bd<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">hasChildNodes</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n   <span class=\"token comment\">// Nun werden wir die Eigenschaft childNodes auslesen</span>\n   <span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> nodeList <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> bd<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>childNodes<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n   <span class=\"token keyword\">for</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> i <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> i <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span> nodeList<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>length<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> i<span class=\"token operator\">++</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n     <span class=\"token comment\">// So wird nodeList durchlaufen und folgender Code wird an jedem Eintrag ausgeführt</span>\n     <span class=\"token comment\">// In diesem Fall soll der Name ausgegeben werden</span>\n     <span class=\"token function\">alert</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>nodeList<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>i<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>nodeName<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n   <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<p><br>\n Diese Liste ist ständig aktuell. Jede Änderung am referenz-Element (hier <code>&lt;body&gt;</code>) bewirkt eine aktualisierung der Liste.<br>\n Wenn Sie also beispielsweise das erste Element in der Liste löschen, rückt automatisch das zweite Element an Stelle des Ersten.<br>\n Deshalb lassen sich z.B. auf diese Art alle Kindknoten eines Elements löschen:</p>\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush:javascript notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token keyword\">while</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>bd<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>firstChild<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    bd<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">removeChild</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>bd<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>firstChild<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"notes","title":"Anmerkungen","isH3":true,"content":"<p>Mit <code>childNodes</code> erhalten Sie eine Liste <strong>aller</strong> Kindknoten, <strong>einschließlich</strong> derer vom Typ <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CharacterData\"><code>CharacterData</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>. Wenn Sie diese Datenknoten nicht im Index haben wollen, verwenden Sie statt <code>childNodes</code> die Eigenschaft <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Element/children\"><code>Element.children</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>.</p>\n<p>Die Einträge in <var><code>nodeList</code></var> sind Objekte, keine Zeichenketten. Für diese Objekte gelten wiederum alle Methoden und Eigenschaften von <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/Node\"><code>Node</code></a>. Um also Daten aus diesen Objekten auszulesen, müssen deren Eigenschaften ausgelesen werden. Um beispielsweise den Namen eines in <var><code>nodeList</code></var> aufgeführten Elements auszulesen, muss man die eigenschaft <code>nodeName</code> auslesen:</p>\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush:javascript notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> name <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> nodeList<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>i<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>nodeName<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>Das <code>document</code> Objekt hat zwei Kindknoten: Die <code>Doctype</code>-Deklaration und das <code>root</code>-Element, das eine Eigenschaft von <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/Document\"><code>Document</code></a> ist.<br>\n Folgendermaßen kann darauf zugegriffen werden:</p>\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush:javascript notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> root <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> document<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>documentElement<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>In (X)HTML-Dokumenten stellt das <code>HTML</code>-Element das <code>root</code>-Element dar.</p>\n<h4 id=\"see_also\" name=\"See_Also\">Siehe auch</h4>\n<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/Node\"><code>Node</code></a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/Node/firstChild\"><code>Node.firstChild</code></a></li>\n <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Node/nodeName\"><code>Node.nodeName</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Element/children\"><code>Element.children</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CharacterData\"><code>CharacterData</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"specification","title":"Spezifikationen","isH3":true,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a class=\"external\" href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/2000/REC-DOM-Level-2-Core-20001113/core.html#ID-1451460987\" rel=\" noopener\">W3C DOM 2 Core: childNodes</a> (en)</li>\n <li><a class=\"external\" href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/2004/REC-DOM-Level-3-Core-20040407/core.html#ID-1451460987\" rel=\" noopener\">W3C DOM 3 Core: childNodes</a> (en)</li>\n <li><a class=\"external\" href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/2004/REC-DOM-Level-3-Core-20040407/core.html#ID-536297177\" rel=\" noopener\">W3C DOM 3 NodeList interface</a> (en)</li>\n</ul>\n<p></p>"}}],"toc":[],"summary":"childNodes gibt eine NodeList (en-US), welche alle Kindknoten (childNodes) eines bestimmten HTML-Elements enthält, zurück.","popularity":0.0003,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"Node.childNodes","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"Node.childNodes","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"element.childNodes","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"Node.childNodes","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"element.childNodes","locale":"ko","native":"한국어"},{"title":"element.childNodes","locale":"pl","native":"Polski"},{"title":"Node.childNodes","locale":"pt-BR","native":"Português (do Brasil)"},{"title":"Node.childNodes","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"},{"title":"Node.childNodes","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"},{"title":"Node.childNodes","locale":"zh-TW","native":"正體中文 (繁體)"}],"source":{"folder":"de/web/api/node/childnodes","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/de/web/api/node/childnodes/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/de/docs/Web","title":"Webtechnologien für Entwickler"},{"uri":"/de/docs/Web/API","title":"Web API Referenz"},{"uri":"/de/docs/Web/API/Node","title":"Node"},{"uri":"/de/docs/Web/API/Node/childNodes","title":"Node.childNodes"}],"pageTitle":"Node.childNodes - Web API Referenz | MDN","noIndexing":false}}